PHP
---
It stands for PHP Hypertext Preprocessor
The scripts are executed on the server

PHP can:
	1) generate dynamic web content
	2) create, open, read, write, delete and close files on the server
	3) collect form data
	4) send and receive cookies
	5) be used to control user-access
	6) encrypt data
	7) add, delete, modify data in your database

Why PHP:
	1) runs on various platforms
	2) supports almost all servers
	3) supports multiple databases
	4) free, easy to learn, efficient
